50,000 or 100,000 yuan if you can. If not, 20,000 or 30,000 yuan will do.

53
00:04:43,780 --> 00:04:45,466
50,000 or 100,000 yuan?

54
00:04:45,466 --> 00:04:49,460
10,000 or 20,000 yuan will do. It doesn't matter how much.

55
