- Man. 
 - Don't touch me!

76
00:06:01,450 --> 00:06:04,720
 - Sorry. 
 - Don't touch me! 

77
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:07,940
I was wrong.

78
00:06:07,940 --> 00:06:09,400
Stay away from me.

79
