140
00:12:58,600 --> 00:13:02,200
Instead of wasting my time with someone who doesn't deserve it,

141
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:05,420
I'll trade it for something that makes me happy.

142
00:13:14,160 --> 00:13:16,560
Thanks for buying me a Coke.

143
