165
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:45,110
It's not as bad as it is in my hometown.

166
00:14:45,110 --> 00:14:47,020
It's a good city to live in.

167
00:14:47,020 --> 00:14:49,620
I'll work at a pharmaceutical company as a researcher.

168
00:14:49,620 --> 00:14:51,933
