 - Call me Dr. Gong.

231
00:18:39,190 --> 00:18:41,133
I was a tech major too.

232
00:18:41,133 --> 00:18:42,810
You're Jing, right?

233
00:18:42,810 --> 00:18:46,522
Before I came here, I heard from Jiang Sen that you're still in undergraduate studies.

234
00:18:46,522 --> 00:18:49,850
What a young talent. Congratulations.

235
00:18:49,850 --> 00:18:52,150
Young man, you'll have a bright future.

236
00:18:52,150 --> 00:18:54,100
