237
00:18:56,720 --> 00:18:59,540
- Happy graduation! 
 - Happy graduation!

238
00:19:02,920 --> 00:19:04,422
I've finally graduated.

239
00:19:04,422 --> 00:19:09,055
Chen Huan Er, congratulations on getting accepted into your ideal grad program.

240
00:19:09,055 --> 00:19:10,280
