242
00:19:15,260 --> 00:19:16,990
- Dig in now. 
 - Okay.

243
00:19:16,990 --> 00:19:19,200
Come on, give me your bowl.

244
00:19:23,755 --> 00:19:25,300
Here you go.

245
00:19:27,100 --> 00:19:30,920
