249
00:19:41,886 --> 00:19:45,150
You have to wash your socks by yourself and on time.

250
00:19:45,150 --> 00:19:47,990
 I hope you'll carefully consider the company's decision 

251
00:19:47,990 --> 00:19:50,540
 to bring Yangwu to the headquarters in Beijing. 

252
00:19:50,540 --> 00:19:52,280
