00:32:45,940 --> 00:32:47,011
   

448
00:32:57,540 --> 00:32:59,620
We're going back to Wuan tomorrow.

449
00:32:59,620 --> 00:33:02,253
Is there anywhere else you'd like to go?

450
00:33:08,520 --> 00:33:10,430
What's wrong?

451
00:33:10,430 --> 00:33:12,150
Jing Xi Chi,

452
00:33:12,820 --> 00:33:15,100
you should stay.

453
00:33:16,710 --> 00:33:21,260
If you come back to Wuan with me, you'll have regrets.

454
00:33:22,230 --> 00:33:25,850
But I don't want those regrets to be because of me.

455
00:33:33,670 --> 00:33:38,030
What if I make the wrong choice?

456
00:33:39,540 --> 00:33:42,340
If it's wrong,

457
00:33:42,340 --> 00:33:44,820
we'll correct it together.

458
00:33:46,430 --> 00:33:48,300
We're still young.

459
00:33:48,300 --> 00:33:51,920
We still have time, right?

460
00:34:17,977 --> 00:34:20,140
I'll pack some thick coats for you.

461
00:34:20,140 --> 00:34:22,177
Remember to wear them at night when you're there.

462
00:34:22,177 --> 00:34:23,955
Large diurnal temperature variation.

463
00:34:23,955 --> 00:34:26,311
You have to remember to wear coats.

464
00:34:28,270 --> 00:34:31,330
Is this T-shirt okay? I'll pack it for you.

465
00:34:33,480 --> 00:34:36,400
 They just transferred you without prior notice. 

466
00:34:36,400 --> 00:34:38,420
 It was so sudden! 

467
00:34:38,420 --> 00:34:42,180
 Li Qiang, I told you to bring more sweaters, but you didn't. 

468
00:34:42,180 --> 00:34:46,211
 It's just a quick check-in. No need to bring so much! 

469
00:35:00,620 --> 00:35:02,960
Remember to eat more.

470
00:35:08,520 --> 00:35:10,370
What's wrong?

471
00:35:25,210 --> 00:35:29,310
I'll come to see you once I'm off on May 1st, okay?

472
00:35:35,210 --> 00:35:38,140
What are you doing? Stop it.

473
00:35:47,270 --> 00:35:48,930
Coming.

474
00:35:49,930 --> 00:35:51,870
Hi! I'm here.

475
00:35:51,870 --> 00:35:53,666
- Leave it to me. 
 - I can do it. Let me do it.

476
00:35:53,666 --> 00:35:55,044
- I'll change my shoes. 
 - Here.

477
00:35:55,044 --> 00:35:56,280
Change them.

478
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:58,270
You've got it all ready. You're heading out?

479
00:35:58,270 --> 00:35:59,470
- I'm going to work. 
 - Okay.

480
00:35:59,470 --> 00:36:01,950
Here you go. I put the key here for you. Help yourself.

481
00:36:01,950 --> 00:36:03,430
Okay.

482
00:36:03,430 --> 00:36:05,450
- I'm leaving. 
 - Bye.

483
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:17,580
I'd like to introduce you to these three from the Wu'an Yangwu team.

484
00:36:17,580 --> 00:36:20,440
Jing Xi Chi, Fu Ying, and Zhou Ye.

485
00:36:20,440 --> 00:36:23,930
Today you are officially joining our family.

486
00:36:28,180 --> 00:36:31,620
First of all, I would like to thank Mr. Gong for appreciating Yangwu

487
00:36:31,620 --> 00:36:35,620
and giving our team a chance to learn from so many excellent seniors.

488
00:36:35,620 --> 00:36:37,910
I hope we can work together happily in the future.

489
00:36:37,910 --> 00:36:39,370
Thank you.

490
00:36:40,760 --> 00:36:43,250
Let's save the formalities for later.

491
00:36:43,250 --> 00:36:48,180
Next, let me introduce the future development plan of Yangwu.

492
00:36:48,180 --> 00:36:51,960
We are going to expand the scale of Yangwu.

493
00:36:51,960 --> 00:36:54,440
Yangwu used to be a second-hand book dealer.

494
00:36:54,440 --> 00:36:56,960
Now we are ready to integrate

495
00:36:56,960 --> 00:37:00,850
with publishers' direct sales of e-books and physical books.

496
00:37:00,850 --> 00:37:04,880
By the end of this year, we'll complete the transformation to selling all kinds of books.

497
00:37:04,880 --> 00:37:07,020
I've already gone through this plan.

498
00:37:07,020 --> 00:37:10,223
I've also presented it to our planning team.

499
00:37:10,223 --> 00:37:14,690
It's very likely to be approved.

500
00:37:14,690 --> 00:37:16,564
This plan...

501
00:37:16,564 --> 00:37:19,266
In response to today's discussion,

502
00:37:19,266 --> 00:37:20,530
hand it over to the teams.

503
00:37:20,530 --> 00:37:21,988
- Dr. Gong. 
 - Let them...

504
00:37:21,988 --> 00:37:23,900
Get back to your work.

505
00:37:25,430 --> 00:37:28,060
Dr. Gong, the plan you just mentioned

506
00:37:28,060 --> 00:37:31,910
seems to be a bit different from what you told us at the beginning.

507
00:37:31,910 --> 00:37:34,080
This plan is the result of the joint research

508
00:37:34,080 --> 00:37:38,026
of several colleagues with rich experience in related products at the headquarters,

509
00:37:38,026 --> 00:37:40,730
which can be said to be very well-developed and mature.

510
00:37:40,730 --> 00:37:42,220
I know.

511
00:37:42,220 --> 00:37:45,310
But if we revise it according to this plan,

512
00:37:45,310 --> 00:37:47,180
Yangwu will lose its unique character.

513
00:37:47,180 --> 00:37:49,910
It'll become indistinguishable from competitors.

514
00:37:49,910 --> 00:37:52,060
Jing, I'm really optimistic about Yangwu,

515
00:37:52,060 --> 00:37:55,020
but you see its limitations too.

516
00:37:55,020 --> 00:37:58,890
If we don't transform it, with its daily activity, it's hard to break through.

517
00:37:58,890 --> 00:38:03,220
I'm sure you don't want to see it remain a half-formed product, right?

518
00:38:03,220 --> 00:38:04,850
Dr. Gong.

519
00:38:09,500 --> 00:38:13,950
Dr. Gong, well, if I could give you a better plan,

520
00:38:13,950 --> 00:38:17,040
would you consider not transforming first?

521
00:38:17,040 --> 00:38:19,220
Jing, I admire you.

522
00:38:19,220 --> 00:38:22,480
But in business, a company needs a product to make a profit.

523
00:38:22,480 --> 00:38:27,080
You've read the terms and conditions of the acquisition by Huan Dao, right?

524
00:38:28,080 --> 00:38:31,120
The headquarters has the right to make decisions.

525
00:38:31,120 --> 00:38:32,730
I know.

526
00:38:32,730 --> 00:38:37,100
But... I still don't want to betray the original vision.

527
00:38:37,100 --> 00:38:40,444
